# inter-domain-simlab bastion sshd config.
# Key-only player entry, locked to the menu. No passwords, no root, no shell:
# ForceCommand runs the menu for every session (the menu itself permits a bundle
# scp from /bundles by inspecting SSH_ORIGINAL_COMMAND). authorized_keys is
# bind-mounted per deploy (StrictModes off so a root-owned read-only mount works).
PermitRootLogin no
PasswordAuthentication no
PermitEmptyPasswords no
PubkeyAuthentication yes
AuthorizedKeysFile .ssh/authorized_keys
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
KbdInteractiveAuthentication no
UsePAM no
StrictModes no
PrintMotd no
AllowTcpForwarding no
X11Forwarding no
PermitTunnel no
ForceCommand /usr/local/bin/menu
